{"tid":700083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫】3Cap帽男擸棒球棍 掃九龍城酒吧","createTime":"2018-06-13T05:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T05:11:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a490037d79e2ac8d16f99f244a75cd70bb133699","tid":700083,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180613/20419383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F20419383&d=8RTelL83%2BhILtVv%2FCeYAPp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f133d707\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F20419383&h=f0a835f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180613/20419383</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月13日 <br />\n<br />\n【動畫】3Cap帽男擸棒球棍<br />\n掃九龍城酒吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】九龍城沙浦道一間酒吧，昨晚凌晨4時許，3名戴口罩及鴨舌帽、手持棒球棍男子衝入店內，不由分說，搗亂推翻店內枱椅、用球棒打碎兩部電視螢幕等，顧客見狀走避，惡漢掃場後，跳上接應私家車逃去。<br />\n<br />\n40歲姓劉負責人報警，點算後損失約8,400元財物，警員將案件列作刑事毀壞案件處理。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n冷氣技工墮地　開腦兩次性命垂危<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【動畫】12歲女攝車罅　捱的士撞"}]}